highlights.text: “Relación - Remix” by Sech, Daddy Yankee, J Balvin, ROSALÍA, and Farruko is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #40.
“POPSTAR (feat. Drake)” by DJ Khaled and Drake is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 60 spots at #20.
Juice WRLD has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Come & Go (with Marshmello)” is the highest at #23.
“Shape of You” by Ed Sheeran has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 192 weeks straight.
